#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:14
msgid "Regional Startup Support Program"
msgstr "Startaplarni qo'llab-quvvatlash dasturi"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:125
msgid "Submit application"
msgstr "Arizani yuborish"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:132
msgid "About the Program"
msgstr "Dastur haqida"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:133
msgid ""
"This hybrid program is designed to empower regional youth through a "
"structured mix of offline bootcamps, online mentorship sessions, and final "
"demo events. We are looking for dedicated youth teams with early-stage "
"digital entrepreneurship ideas and a working prototype."
msgstr ""
"Ushbu gibrid dastur hududiy yoshlarning imkoniyatlarini kengaytirish uchun "
"mo'ljallangan bo'lib, u oflayn butkemplar, onlayn mentorlik sessiyalari va "
"yakuniy demo tadbirlarini o'z ichiga oladi. Dastur raqamli tadbirkorlik "
"sohasida boshlang'ich bosqichdagi g'oyalari va ishchi prototipiga ega "
"bo'lgan intiluvchan yoshlar jamoalarini izlaydi."

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:137
msgid "Who Can Apply"
msgstr "Kimlar ariza topshirishi mumkin?"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:138
msgid ""
"Teams based in Surkhandarya, Ferghana, Andijan, and Namangan. The program "
"will select an initial cohort of 40 startup teams."
msgstr ""
"Surxondaryo, Fargʻona, Andijon va Namangan viloyatlarida joylashgan "
"jamoalar. Dastur doirasida dastlabki 40 ta startap jamoasi saralab olinadi."

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:144
msgid "Program Team"
msgstr "Dastur jamoasi"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:145
msgid ""
"Our Program Team is a dedicated collective of mentors and ecosystem builders "
"committed to bridging the gap between a regional idea and a market-ready "
"digital product."
msgstr "Dastur jamoasi — g‘oyalar va bozorga tayyor raqamli mahsulotlar o‘rtasidagi farqni bartaraf etishga intiluvchi mentorlar hamda ekotizim yaratuvchilarining birdam jamoasidir."

