#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:170
msgid "Program Timeline and Key Dates"
msgstr "Muhim sanalar"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:172
msgid "Application Deadline:"
msgstr "Ariza topshirish muddati:"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:172
msgid "April 10, 2026"
msgstr "10 Aprel, 2026"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:173
msgid "Offline Bootcamps:"
msgstr "Oflayn (yuzma-yuz) butkemplar:"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:173
msgid ""
"April 16-17 in Termez, and April 23-24 in Ferghana. These intensive 2-day "
"workshops focus on customer development, MVP design, and Lean startup "
"methodologies."
msgstr "16-17-aprel Termizda va 23-24-aprel Farg‘onada. Ushbu 2 kunlik intensiv mashg'ulotlar mijozlarni topish (cusdev), MVPni ishalb chiqish va Lean startup metodologiyasini o'rganishga qaratilgan."

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:174
msgid "Online Mentorship:"
msgstr "Onlayn (masofaviy) mentorlik:"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:174
msgid ""
"Late April to early May, featuring specialized modules on Sales/Marketing, "
"Financial Modelling, AI for Startups, and Fundraising/Working with VCs."
msgstr "Aprel oyining oxiridan may oyining boshigacha: Sotuv/Marketing, Moliyaviy modellashtirish, Startaplar uchun AI (Sun'iy intellekt) hamda Investitsiya jalb qilish (Fundraising) va venchur kapitalistlar (VC) bilan ishlash bo'yicha maxsus modullar."

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:175
msgid "Demo Days:"
msgstr "Demo kunlari:"

#: .\templates\startup_support_program.html:175
msgid ""
"May 13-14 in Termez, and May 25-26 in Ferghana. Teams will pitch their "
"polished ideas to local ecosystem partners and venture capital "
"representatives."
msgstr "13-14-may Termizda va 25-26-may Farg‘onada. Jamoalar o‘zlarining shakllantirilgan g‘oyalarini mahalliy ekotizim hamkorlari va venchur kapital vakillariga taqdim etadilar (pitch qiladilar)."
